name: SIGIL OF JUBILÆUM
description:
Rejoice, sinners!
This is your last chance of redemption. 
After centuries the requirements have finally been met and the year of jubilee is finally upon us. 
Like a golden gift from god, may all your sins and guilt be washed away from your tainted soul.

800x800gif mouse drawn on a Deluxe Paint emulator for the MS-DOS
